Introduction

Base URL: http://api.nongjangs.com.test

This documentation aims to provide all the information you need to work with our API.

As you scroll, you'll see code examples for working with the API in different programming languages in the dark area to the right (or as part of the content on mobile). You can switch the language used with the tabs at the top right (or from the nav menu at the top left on mobile).

Authenticating requests

This API is not authenticated.

User

Qna(문의)


생성

POST
http://api.nongjangs.com.test
/api/qnas

Body Parameters

qna_category_id
integer
required
title
string
required

제목. Must not be greater than 500 characters.

description
string
required

내용. Must not be greater than 10000 characters.

imgs
object

이미지 목록 input-images 사용.

Example response:
{
    "data": [
        {
            "id": "고유번호",
            "title": "제목",
            "description": "내용",
            "qnaCategory": "qna 유형 객체",
            "imgs": "이미지 목록",
            "answer": "답변",
            "format_created_at": "표시용 생성일자",
            "format_answered_at": "표시용 답변일자"
        }
    ],
    "meta": {
        "total": "총 개수",
        "current_page": "현재 페이지",
        "last_page": "마지막 페이지"
    }
}
